<m:mo> = </m:mo> 
<m:mi> g </m:mi>
<m:mi> t </m:mi>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-68">
Substituting in the equation above :
</para>
<para id="element-69">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:mo> ⇒ </m:mo> 
<m:mi> ℓ </m:mi>
