</m:msup>

</m:math>
 is a constant and the same can be taken out of differentiation,
</para>
<para id="element-113"><equation id="equation-113">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:msub>
<m:mo> t </m:mo> 
